name: Dragon
description: The Eastern dragon, an emblem of power, wisdom, and wealth, embodies the essence of Eastern nations. It signifies not only good fortune and dignity but also harmony and strength. With the launch of a 'Dragon Culture' themed meme coin, our goal is to elevate and share this distinct and rich cultural legacy on a global stage, providing an opportunity for the world to gain a deeper understanding and appreciation of this gem of Eastern culture.
